    "title": "Sending messages to players in turn-based games"
  },
  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "GameKit provides several APIs for you to communicate events and send messages in your turn-based games. You can include a message and custom game data in the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.gamekit/documentation/GameKit/GKTurnBasedMatch",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " object passed between active participants. You can also send a notification to other participants when they’re not running your game.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To send other types of data between players when they’re not taking their turn, see the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.gamekit/documentation/GameKit/GKTurnBasedExchange",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " class.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": " ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "The code listings in this article use GameKit asynchronous methods that you invoke from an ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "code": "async",
                  "type": "codeVoice"
                },
                {
                  "text": " method or within a ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "code": "Task",
                  "type": "codeVoice"
                },
                {
                  "text": " structure. For details on asynchronous flows, see ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "identifier": "https://docs.swift.org/swift-book/LanguageGuide/Concurrency.html",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "type": "reference"
                },
                {
                  "text": ".",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name": "Important",
          "style": "important",
          "type": "aside"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Pass-messages-from-the-current-participant",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Pass messages from the current participant",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You can send localized or non-localized messages from the current participant to others in a turn-based match using the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.gamekit/documentation/GameKit/GKTurnBasedMatch",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " object. If the game isn’t running or is in the background, the message you provide appears immediately at the top of the screen as a notification. If the game is in the foreground, get the message from the match object GameKit passes to participants and display it in your own interface.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Before you perform an action such as ending a turn, set the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.gamekit/documentation/GameKit/GKTurnBasedMatch/message",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " property of the match object. Alternatively, set a message that GameKit localizes using the receiving participant’s language and region settings using the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.gamekit/documentation/GameKit/GKTurnBasedMatch/setLocalizableMessageWithKey(_:arguments:)",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " method.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "code": [
            "match.message = \"We're all counting on you!\"",
            "try await match.endTurn(withNextParticipants: nextParticipants, turnTimeout: GKTurnTimeoutDefault, match: gameData)"
          ],
          "syntax": "swift",
          "type": "codeListing"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "If a participant taps the notification when it appears, GameKit launches the game or brings it to the foreground. GameKit invokes the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "GKTurnBasedEventListener",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.gamekit/documentation/GameKit/GKTurnBasedEventListener/player(_:receivedTurnEventFor:didBecomeActive:)",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " protocol method passing ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/swift/true",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " as the active parameter. Implement this method to join the match. For more information on handling turn-based events, see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.gamekit/documentation/GameKit/starting-turn-based-matches-and-passing-turns-between-players",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "If the game is in the foreground, GameKit invokes this method but passes ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/swift/false",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " as the active parameter. You can then present the message in your own interface by getting the message from the match object using the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.gamekit/documentation/GameKit/GKTurnBasedMatch/message",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " property.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To localize a message, add the key you pass to the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.gamekit/documentation/GameKit/GKTurnBasedMatch/setLocalizableMessageWithKey(_:arguments:)",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " method and a placeholder translation to a ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": ".strings",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " file in your project (for example, the default ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "Localizable.strings",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " file). For more information on adapting your game for different languages and regions, see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Xcode/localization",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Send-messages-from-any-participant",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Send messages from any participant",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Send a localized message from any participant to others using a Game Center notification. For example, send a reminder to the current participant from another participant who is waiting for them to take their turn. GameKit sends the reminder to the participants as a push notification that doesn’t interrupt their gameplay. The notification only appears when the game isn’t running — it doesn’t appear if the participant runs the game in either the foreground or background.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "identifier": "media-3894240",
              "type": "image"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To display the GameKit notification:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Invoke the ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "GKTurnBasedMatch",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.gamekit/documentation/GameKit/GKTurnBasedMatch/sendReminder(to:localizableMessageKey:arguments:completionHandler:)",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " method passing the participants and a localized message key:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "orderedList"
        },
        {
          "code": [
            "// Create an array that contains the current participant.",
            "let participants = match.participants.filter {",
            "    $0 == match.currentParticipant",
            "}",
            "",
            "// Send a reminder to the current participant.",
            "try await match.sendReminder(to: participants, localizableMessageKey: \"It's your turn to play.\", arguments: [])"
          ],
          "syntax": "swift",
          "type": "codeListing"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Add the localized message key and placeholder translation to a  ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": ".strings",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " file in your project. If necessary, add a ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": ".strings",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " file (for example, the default ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "Localizable.strings",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " file) to your project and make it localizable. For the Xcode steps, see ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Xcode/adding-resources-to-localizations",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " and ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "Editing XLIFF and strings files",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ".",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "start": 2,
          "type": "orderedList"
        },
        {
          "code": [
            "\"It's your turn to play.\" = \"It's your turn to play.\";"
          ],
          "syntax": "swift",
          "type": "codeListing"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "When the player taps the notification, GameKit invokes the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "GKTurnBasedEventListener",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.gamekit/documentation/GameKit/GKTurnBasedEventListener/player(_:receivedTurnEventFor:didBecomeActive:)",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " protocol method passing ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/swift/true",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " as the active parameter. Implement this method to join the existing match. For more information on handling turn-based events, see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.gamekit/documentation/GameKit/starting-turn-based-matches-and-passing-turns-between-players",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": " ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "If you exceed the system’s 10-minute limit for the frequency of sending reminders, a ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "code": "GKServerTurnBasedMaxSessionOtherError",
                  "type": "codeVoice"
                },
                {
                  "text": " error occurs.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name": "Note",
          "style": "note",
          "type": "aside"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
